ls disks/
CP009279.scexe*
CP010297.scexe*
CP011102.scexe*
CP011615.scexe*

Notes:
CP*.scexe are HP firmware binaries. You need to download them from hp.com.
libstdc++2.10-glibc2.2_2.95.4-27_i386.deb is needed on amd64 hosts. Get it 
from your local Debian mirror and dpkg --force-architecture -i it before 
running firmware.sh.
